      "updatedAt": 1749513702000
    },
    {
      "id": "n-ba1",
      "mapId": "q-bornagain",
      "type": "note",
      "content": "A thought I keep returning to: an everlasting priest serves a people given everlasting life. Maybe 'born again' is the doorway into the very life His priesthood secures.",
      "position": {
        "x": 760,
        "y": 0
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513703000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513703000
    },
    {
      "id": "anchor-spirit",
      "mapId": "q-spirit",
      "type": "question",
      "content": "What is Jesus saying about the Spirit and the wind?",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513709000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513709000
    },
    {
      "id": "v-john37",
      "mapId": "q-spirit",
      "type": "verse",
      "content": "",
      "position": {
        "x": -360,
        "y": 210
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513710000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513710000,
      "verseRef": "John 3:7",
      "verseText": "Do not be amazed that I said, ‘You must be born again.’"
    },
    {
      "id": "v-john38",
      "mapId": "q-spirit",
      "type": "verse",
      "content": "",
      "position": {
        "x": 360,
        "y": 210
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513711000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513711000,
      "verseRef": "John 3:8",
      "verseText": "The wind blows where it wishes. You hear its sound, but you do not know where it comes from or where it is going. So it is with everyone born of the Spirit.”"
    },
    {
      "id": "v-1pet123",
      "mapId": "q-spirit",
      "type": "verse",
      "content": "",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 330
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513712000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513712000,
      "verseRef": "1 Peter 1:23",
      "verseText": "For you have been born again, not of perishable seed, but of imperishable, through the living and enduring word of God."
    },
    {
      "id": "n-sp1",
      "mapId": "q-spirit",
      "type": "note",
      "content": "I love that the same word means wind and Spirit. You don't see the wind — only what it moves. That's about the most honest picture of new birth I can think of.",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": -300
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513713000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513713000
    },
    {
      "id": "anchor-abraham",
      "mapId": "q-abraham",
      "type": "question",
      "content": "Why does Abraham's response to Melchizedek matter so much?",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513718000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513718000
    },
    {
      "id": "v-gen156",
      "mapId": "q-abraham",
      "type": "verse",
      "content": "",
      "position": {
        "x": -390,
        "y": 200
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513719000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513719000,
      "verseRef": "Genesis 15:6",
      "verseText": "Abram believed the LORD, and it was credited to him as righteousness."
    },
    {
      "id": "v-rom43",
      "mapId": "q-abraham",
      "type": "verse",
      "content": "",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 320
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513720000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513720000,
      "verseRef": "Romans 4:3",
      "verseText": "For what does the Scripture say? “Abraham believed God, and it was credited to him as righteousness.”"
    },
    {
      "id": "v-gal36",
      "mapId": "q-abraham",
      "type": "verse",
      "content": "",
      "position": {
        "x": 390,
        "y": 200
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513721000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513721000,
      "verseRef": "Galatians 3:6",
      "verseText": "So also, “Abraham believed God, and it was credited to him as righteousness.”"
    },
    {
      "id": "n-ab1",
      "mapId": "q-abraham",
      "type": "note",
      "content": "It moves me that Abraham gave a tenth before any law required it — faith first, obligation later. His believing God was credited as righteousness; the tithe was just the overflow.",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": -300
      },
      "createdAt": 1749513722000,
      "updatedAt": 1749513722000
    }
  ],
